==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: maxwell
<hw>maxwell</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A CGS unit of magnetic flux,
abbreviated <abbr>Mx</abbr>; it is equal to the magnetic flux passing
through one square centimeter which is normal to a magnetic field of one
gauss.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Mx.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>May</ent>⟦br⟧
